# Wildlife Photography Gallery

This directory should contain your wildlife photography collection.

## Required Images:
Add 6 or more images named:
- wildlife-1.jpg
- wildlife-2.jpg
- wildlife-3.jpg
- wildlife-4.jpg
- wildlife-5.jpg
- wildlife-6.jpg
- (continue numbering as needed)

## Specifications:
- Dimensions: 1200x1600px or higher (3:4 aspect ratio / portrait)
- Format: JPG (optimized for web, under 300KB each recommended)
- Content: Your best wildlife photography - animals in nature, natural habitats, behavior shots

## How to Add:
1. Select your best wildlife photographs
2. Rename them following the numbering pattern (wildlife-1.jpg, wildlife-2.jpg, etc.)
3. Place them in `/public/photos/wildlife/`
4. If adding more than 6, also update `/app/portfolio/[category]/page.tsx` to include additional photo entries

The gallery will display these in a responsive 3-column grid on desktop, 2 columns on tablet, and 1 column on mobile.
